## External Scripts (Out-of-LLM Processing)

The following scripts handle deterministic tasks:

### build_index.py
- Scans repository
- Generates file_index.json
- Records file paths and metadata

### summarize_files.py
- Reads files
- Generates short summaries
- Stores in summary_index.json

### Why Scripts Are Used:
- Faster than LLM
- No token cost
- Deterministic results

### Agent Usage:
The agent assumes these scripts have already been run before analysis.
